<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='289477' id='t-289477'>to one where sharing is power.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='292423' id='t-292423'>It was the fundamental shift,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='294395' id='t-294395'>not new tactics, not new weapons,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='296733' id='t-296733'>not new anything else.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='298037' id='t-298037'>It was the idea that we were now part of a team</span>
