<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:18
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='307661' id='t-307661'>And I want everybody to take a deep breath</span>
