<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='314299' id='t-314299'>that leaks out you're not going to like.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='316631' id='t-316631'>Somebody's going to get my college grades out,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='318877' id='t-318877'>a that's going to be a disaster. (Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='322904' id='t-322904'>But it's going to be okay, and I will tell you that</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='326273' id='t-326273'>I am more scared of the bureaucrat</span>
